Package: Informeasure
Type: Package
Title: R implementation of Information measures
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Chu PAN
Maintainer: Chu PAN <chu.pan@hnu.edu.cn>
Description: This package compiles most information measures currently available: mutual information, conditional mutual information, interaction information, 
partial information decomposition and part mutual information. The first estimator is used to infer bivariate network while the estimation of the last four are 
dedicated to the identification of trivariate network. 
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
